
Web Storage:

    - Web Storage allows to store some information locally on the user's computer.
    - Similiar to Cookies, but it is faster and much better than cookies.

Type of Web Storage:

    1. Local Storage

    - Local Storage stores the data for your website on permanent basis.
    - THat means, data will be available on the next day, the next week or untill you remve it.

    2. Session Storage

    - Session Storage stores the data for your website on temporary basis.
    - That means, data will disappear when sessions ends i.e. 
    - When you navigate to another window or tab.

